<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="interview-vt">interview <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɪntəvjuː/    美 /'ɪntəvjuː/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>采访；面试；会见：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was <strong>interviewing</strong> a woman villager <strong>for</strong> an article.
我当时正为一篇报道采访一名村妇。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>interviewed</strong> ten people <strong>for</strong> the job. 
这个职位我们面试了10个人。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>interviewee /ˌɪntəvjuː'iː/ n [C]<br />
interviewer  /'ɪntəvjuːə(r)/ n [C]   </p></div>